headline: Sutter Health and GE HealthCare enter strategic partnership to benefit patients, physicians and clinicians with advanced, AI-powered imaging
summary: SACRAMENTO, Calif., January 14, 2025--Sutter Health and GE HealthCare (Nasdaq: GEHC) today announced a seven-year strategic enterprise partnership, known as a Care Alliance, that aims to increase access to innovative imaging services and create a more seamless and coordinated experience for clinicians and patients across the Sutter Health system.
